properties.name: Track Mafia
properties.message: Track Mafia: Thursdays at 6:30pm, Paddington Recreation Ground W9 1PF. Free track training in 4-week blocks. All abilities welcome, bag drop available.

properties.name: Your Friendly Runners
properties.message: Your Friendly Runners: Saturdays at 9am, Lodestar Coffee E5 8EE. East London-based friendly running group for all abilities. Bag drop available.

properties.name: One Track
properties.message: One Track: Thursday at 6:30pm, Duke of York Square SW3 4LY. Track runs in Chelsea led by coach Fletch. All abilities welcome, bag drop on site.

properties.name: Pure Sport Run Club
properties.message: Pure Sport Run Club: Wednesday at 6:15pm, Battersea Park Track Entrance/Pure Sport HQ (alternate weeks). Weekly social 5k of intervals plus monthly track night. All abilities welcome, bag drop available.

properties.name: Tempo Run Club
properties.message: Tempo run club: Tuesday at 6:45pm, Peckham Levels SE15 4ST. Community of musicians and DJs in South London. Free weekly run for all abilities, bag drop and open deck DJ sets.

properties.name: Mafia Moves
properties.message: Mafia Moves: Tuesday at 6.30pm, Beaverton Corner Pin N17 0AG, and Saturday at 9:30am, Tottenham Stadium. Weekly runs for all abilities in north London led by coach Andre. Free sessions with bag drop available.

properties.name: Grove Lane Runners
properties.message: Grove lane runners: Wednesday at 7:30am and Sunday at 8:45am, Govelane Deli SE5 8SY. Friendly 5's on Sundays and mid-week miles on Wednesdays in south London. All abilities welcome, bag drop available.

properties.name: Tracksmith Run Clubs
properties.message: Tracksmith Run Clubs: Various locations in London. Several weekly run clubs led by coach Amrit. Check Tracksmith Strava for event details.
properties.timetable: Various times, check Tracksmith Strava for details

properties.name: Solemother
properties.message: Solemother: Various locations. Super fun, sassy, and supportive social exercise group for women. Activities include runs, hikes, swims, classes, and social events.

properties.name: Run Talk Run
properties.message: Run Talk Run: Various locations across the UK. Running group and mental health support community. Casual jogs and supportive conversations.
properties.timetable: Check website for local group times

properties.name: Park Run UK
properties.message: Park Run UK: Various locations. Free 5K runs every Saturday morning. Register online, print barcode, and join any event worldwide.

properties.name: Run Dem Crew
properties.message: Run Dem Crew: London. Fun running crew with emphasis on community, youth mentoring, and creative endeavors.

properties.name: Midnight Runners
properties.message: Midnight Runners: London. Runs with loud beats, exercise stops, and a party atmosphere. No one left behind policy.

properties.name: WMN RUN
properties.message: WMN RUN: London and Bristol. Mission to bridge the gender gap in running. Regular social runs and race training opportunities.

properties.name: Mikkeller Running Club
properties.message: Mikkeller Running Club: London. Combines running with food and beer. Global operation with a focus on balancing fitness and enjoyment of life.

properties.name: Our Parks
properties.message: Our Parks: Various locations across UK parks. Free fitness classes including running. Focus on accessibility and inclusivity.
properties.timetable: Check website for local class times

properties.name: LDN Slct
properties.message: LDN Slct: Speed sessions on Tuesdays at Paddington Track and Hyde Park for Saturday morning social runs. Headed up by coach Manni.

properties.name: Scrambled Legs
properties.message: Scrambled Legs: Weekly long runs on Saturdays between 20-30k in London. New routes and meeting places each week.

properties.name: Sexy Pace Run Crew
properties.message: Sexy Pace Run Crew: Biweekly women's social runs for beginners and anyone looking to run at a 'sexy pace'. Starting at the On Regent street store for a 5k.

properties.name: Say Yes Club
properties.message: Say Yes Club: Every Tuesday evening at 6:15pm in London Fields for a social 5k. Finish at a pub for social drinks.

properties.name: 10Ironwomen
properties.message: 10Ironwomen: Inclusive female-only run and Triathlon club in London. Striving for a 50/50 split in ironman attendance.

properties.name: Ealing Eagles
properties.message: Ealing Eagles: Friendly, inclusive and diverse running club based in Ealing. Social Monday and Wednesday 7.30pm club runs.
